OxfLinLat141.First Lines:
Agnus dei hodie natus de pura virgineÞe lombe for hys
                    fadyr is chomehe is contyte a pure virgynys wombeConceptus sacro
                        flamme…
OxfLinLat141.Last Lines:
…They offyrd gold myr & solenniteNoue stelle
                    lumine
